      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 14:35:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着利润大幅下滑，美国银行债券交易员的业绩出现意外下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/bofa-bond-traders-post-surprise-drop-as-profit-slumps-by-half</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行(Bank of America Corp.)的盈利未达到预期，因为该行第四季度的众多费用削减了利润，而且该公司的固定收益交易员的收入意外下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/bofa-bond-traders-post-surprise-drop-as-profit-slumps-by-half</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:04:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>富国银行的 FDIC 和遣散费成本超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/wells-fargo-s-costs-exceed-estimates-on-severance-fdic-charge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富国银行该公司第四季度的成本高于预期，原因是遣散费以及去年银行倒闭后该银行为补充联邦存款保险公司主要基金的捐款而增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/wells-fargo-s-costs-exceed-estimates-on-severance-fdic-charge</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:00:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
