      <title>贝莱德卷土重来总资产突破10万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/blackrock-total-assets-top-10-trillion-after-comeback-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司(BlackRock Inc.)的客户在第四季度纷纷买入其长期基金，向ETF和其他产品增持了630亿美元，这表明随着股票和债券市场的飙升，投资者开始投入现金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/blackrock-total-assets-top-10-trillion-after-comeback-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
